---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - AI Developer & Researcher">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          About Me
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Passionate about creating intelligent solutions that make a difference
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Profile Image -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
        <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-24 h-24 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-600">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Professional Background</h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm a full-stack developer and AI researcher with a passion for building 
          intelligent applications that solve real-world problems. My work spans 
          modern web technologies, machine learning, and academic research, with a 
          focus on creating scalable, user-centered solutions.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          With expertise in Python, FastAPI, React, and TypeScript, I create 
          applications that leverage the latest in AI and machine learning. My 
          approach combines technical excellence with practical problem-solving, 
          ensuring that complex technologies are accessible and useful to end users.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 mt-12">Technical Expertise</h3>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Frontend Development</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                React & TypeScript
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                Astro & Static Site Generation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                Tailwind CSS & Responsive Design
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                Modern JavaScript (ES6+)
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Backend & AI</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                Python & FastAPI
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                Machine Learning & AI Integration
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                Vector Databases (Qdrant)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-500 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                OpenAI API & RAG Systems
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Research & Innovation</h3>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          My research focuses on practical applications of artificial intelligence 
          in web development and user experience design. I'm particularly interested 
          in how AI can enhance developer productivity and create more intuitive 
          user interfaces.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Recent work includes developing retrieval-augmented generation systems 
          for domain-specific knowledge bases and exploring novel approaches to 
          automated code generation and testing.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Beyond Code</h3>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          When I'm not coding, you can find me contributing to open-source projects, 
          writing technical articles, or exploring the latest developments in AI and 
          machine learning. I believe in continuous learning and sharing knowledge 
          with the developer community.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I'm always excited to collaborate on innovative projects and explore new 
          technologies. Whether you're looking to build an AI-powered application 
          or need expertise in modern web development, I'd love to discuss how we 
          can work together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">Skills & Technologies</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
        {[
          'Python', 'TypeScript', 'React', 'FastAPI', 'Astro', 'Tailwind CSS',
          'OpenAI', 'Qdrant', 'Git', 'Docker', 'AWS', 'Node.js'
        ].map((skill) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">{skill}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        Let's Build Something Amazing Together
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Ready to discuss your next project or explore collaboration opportunities?
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a 
          href="mailto:your.email@example.com"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary-500 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L2 18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
          </svg>
          Get In Touch
        </a>
        
        <a 
          href="/#projects"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 border border-gray-300 text-base font-medium rounded-lg text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary-500 transition-colors shadow-md hover:shadow-lg"
        >
          View My Work
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>